Goodday Cultured Milk is a probiotic drink developed by Universal Robina Corporation (URC) in collaboration with Asahi Beverages Philippines. This drink is enriched with patented Lactobacillus casei strain Shirota (LcS) to support digestive health. Its smooth texture and slightly tangy taste make it a refreshing and healthy beverage option.
Type of Milk: Cultured probiotic milk
Ideal For: Improving digestion and gut health Individuals seeking a healthy and refreshing drink Families and health-conscious consumers
Ingredients: Water Sugar Skimmed milk Probiotic Lactobacillus casei strain Shirota (LcS) Natural flavors
Storage: Keep refrigerated at 2–8°C. Consume immediately after opening.
Where to buy: Puregold Pasay, SM Supermarkets Cebu
______________________________________________________________________________
Nutrition Facts (Per 100ml) Energy: 70 kcal
Protein: 1g
Carbohydrates: 16g
Fat: 0g
Calcium: 50mg
Probiotic Content: Billions of live Lactobacillus casei
